data.description: Lots of charm! This 3bed 2 bath home is nestled into the hillside w/5 acres and a stunning overlook view of Salt Creek. The 1512 sq home has many updates throughout, vinyl plank floors, fresh paint & the roof, trusses & HVAC were new in 2016 +Septic updated 2019. Relax on the huge covered front porch with a cup of coffee and the birds or maybe a big family BBQ just in time to watch the fall colors. The kitchen is spacious & super cute that has an island and breakfast bar with an open concept to the dining room. Escape to the large primary suite that is separate from the other 2 bedrooms & features a walk in closet and bath with a soaker tub&shower. Oversized 24x40 detached garage. AS IS  possible handicap accessible w/ramp.
